cc:Work.dc:title: Flag and Fist
cc:Work.dc:description: I know this is the war flag (naval flag) of Japan... but I didn't really draw this to be political. I just saw a similar design and thought it was fascinating. Not suppose to be pro-Japan or anti-Japan. It just is what it is. Mostly hand drawn by me, but I used an old public domain photo of a fist as inspiration for this fist.
